        "text": "When forming a learning pod about it is often essential to go slow to go far. During the early days, it's important to wander. This wandering, is a critical part of a group's forming. The pod members need to create time to be curious about each other and to learn to appreciate each voice, each wisdom. Slowly, a collective wisdom will begin to weave together into a larger story of becoming."
